text: Jan Ordoš (born September 18, 1996) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for Bílí Tygři Liberec of the Czech Extraliga. Ordoš made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Bílí Tygři Liberec during the 2015-16 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:HC Bílí Tygři Liberec players Category:Czech ice hockey forwards
